{"tid":2124289,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"內地嚴審童書 港恐步後塵","createTime":"2020-07-25T09:32:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T09:59:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"85bb4c132fbb0fb14dddff28dfd5fe0c3820f24f","tid":2124289,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T09:32:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200724/F3PJ3GD25GGUO2Q3ANFCZHNMVM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200724%2FF3PJ3GD25GGUO2Q3ANFCZHNMVM%2F&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHQjGR3CVFSgRSSfEWrWQqBA%3D&h=a57b2dea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200724%2FF3PJ3GD25GGUO2Q3ANFCZHNMVM%2F&h=da16ab2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200724/F3PJ3GD25GGUO2Q3ANFCZHNMVM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n內地嚴審童書 港恐步後塵<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】童書可培養兒童的普世價值觀，屬當地本土文化，是建立公民身份之端。港版國安法對本港童書出版業的影響尚未浮現，然而內地童書界一早備受政治意識形態掣肘。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/X61AD9lBhi3vJsl3YMKAENwraas=/928x628/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2QFDPUG5L6ZFBFCIYMQIIM2ITA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FX61AD9lBhi3vJsl3YMKAENwraas%3D%2F928x628%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2QFDPUG5L6ZFBFCIYMQIIM2ITA.gif&h=07561c21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n柯佳列指內地嚴格過濾童書，擔心香港出版社也自我審查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「和平」「民主」被消失<br />\n<br />\n本港親子教育團體綠腳丫七。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n柯不時往內地推廣閱讀活動，對內地閱讀文化有深刻觀察。他指內地學校圖書館引入原創與外國圖書的比例須為九比一，題材也受限制，「有十字架的不可放入學校，就算不談政治、民主自由，講外國節日如聖誕節都不可以放入學校。」外交政治也影響出版：「跟韓國關係差，便限制引進（童書）。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/yixUxDN1QBkRumlpNnvAUtVS9Yo=/1902x981/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RLRWLBF5FNTN46DSZ45U6DYWUA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FyixUxDN1QBkRumlpNnvAUtVS9Yo%3D%2F1902x981%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRLRWLBF5FNTN46DSZ45U6DYWUA.gif&h=0d632739&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n濱田桂子所著的《和平是什麼》獲得今年度第13屆香港書獎；此書屬中日韓聯合出版「祈願和平」系列繪本之一，在內地被消失，去年木棉樹買下版權再版，香港兒童才有機會閱。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另一被消失的繪本是台灣作者孫心瑜的《北京遊》。此書講述小女孩穿梭古今北京，在頹垣敗瓦見「拆」字等文革標語，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n柯續指，某些繪本走偏鋒，像大陸首位獲國際安徒生獎的作家曹文軒短篇小說《痴雞》，講述黑雞想當媽媽，動了孵蛋的念頭，卻違背主人賺錢意願。全書只用黑色描摹人物，唯一紅色是纏着母雞的布條，有虐雞畫面，卻無阻黑雞做媽媽的決心。柯訝異此書對象是兒童：「那是文革年代他們（作者、繪者）的童年紀錄，我覺得有（像）文革時『人食人』&hellip;&hellip;當中有不少隱喻。」<br />\n<br />\n國安法來襲，香港儼如提早與大陸接軌。。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"7bc9448b838f89e92949e116f069801c529cd60e","tid":2124289,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T09:51:14.000Z","msg":"倪匡？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46e29ec4dc17da3cb6ae5aa73f46d28dcb22827b","tid":2124289,"uid":83228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T09:59:26.000Z","msg":"講恐怖?呢啲童話同格林原著無得揮<br />\n香港首先無咗議會<br />\n之後無報社書商<br />\n之後無網絡<br />\n<br />\n開始咗就骨牌硬<br />\n不出三年<br />\n香港同大陸城市無異<br />\n<br />\nWw3先有救"}]}